    "title": {
      "rendered": "The Importance of Branding Your Nonprofit on Social Networks Through Graphic Design"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/branding-on-social-networks.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-14155 alignright\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/branding-on-social-networks-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"branding-on-social-networks\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/branding-on-social-networks.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/branding-on-social-networks.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/branding-on-social-networks.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/branding-on-social-networks.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/branding-on-social-networks.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Nonprofits were the early adopters of social networks. The were active on Myspace, YouTube, and creating Facebook Groups long before most of the companies that are often praised for being the pioneers of social media. One of the reasons was that social networks were free to join and lacked monthly fees. Enterprising nonprofit staff (usually GenXers) with a love for the Internet created communities on Myspace, YouTube, and Facebook in 2004/2005 and most often without executive buy-in. They acted on instinct that social networks were going to be transformative\u00a0tools for cause awareness and fundraising campaigns, and they were right. It&#8217;s an entirely different Internet than it was just five years ago.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The conundrum today, however, is that many nonprofits have not moved beyond the concept of social networks being free. The Internet users of 2013 expect polish and professionalism across all your online channels not only in their appearance, but also in how they are managed. A good content strategy requires time and skills to execute and the successful management of your social networks requires training. And quality graphic design for your social networks that strengthens your online brand is also not free unless you are fortunate enough to have a staff person or volunteer skilled in Photoshop. That said, Nonprofit Tech for Good just went through the process of rebranding and below are the most important graphics necessary for your social networks:</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>1. <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/\">An Avatar</a> :: 200 x 200 pixels</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Avatar-250.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-14145\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Avatar-250.png?resize=200%2C200\" alt=\"Avatar-250\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Avatar-250.png?w=250&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Avatar-250.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Avatar-250.png?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Avatar-250.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Your avatar should complement or be extracted from your logo:</strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Logo.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14147\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Logo.jpg?resize=600%2C59\" alt=\"Logo\" width=\"600\" height=\"59\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Logo.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Logo.jpg?resize=300%2C29&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>2. <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\">Facebook Cover</a> :: 851 x 315 pixels</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Facebook-Cover-for-Nonprofits1.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14124\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Facebook-Cover-for-Nonprofits1.jpg?resize=600%2C232\" alt=\"Facebook Cover for Nonprofits\" width=\"600\" height=\"232\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Facebook-Cover-for-Nonprofits1.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Facebook-Cover-for-Nonprofits1.jpg?resize=300%2C116&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/nonprofitorgs\">Twitter Background</a> :: 1920 x 1080 pixels</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Twitter-Background-for-Nonp.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14127\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Twitter-Background-for-Nonp.jpg?resize=600%2C338\" alt=\"Twitter-Background-for-Nonp\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Twitter-Background-for-Nonp.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Twitter-Background-for-Nonp.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Twitter Header (Fixed) ::\u00a0520 x 260 pixels</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Twitter-Header-for-Nonprofi.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14128\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Twitter-Header-for-Nonprofi.jpg?resize=520%2C260\" alt=\"Twitter-Header-for-Nonprofi\" width=\"520\" height=\"260\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Twitter-Header-for-Nonprofi.jpg?w=520&amp;ssl=1 520w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Twitter-Header-for-Nonprofi.jpg?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 520px) 100vw, 520px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Twitter Header (Color) ::\u00a0300 x 300 pixels</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Blue.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14129\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Blue.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Blue\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Blue.jpg?w=300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Blue.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Blue.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Blue.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/b/103858765220369650172/103858765220369650172/posts\">Google+ Banner</a>\u00a0::\u00a02120 x 1192 pixels</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Google%2B-Banner-for-Nonprofi.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14132\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Google%2B-Banner-for-Nonprofi.jpg?resize=600%2C338\" alt=\"Google+-Banner-for-Nonprofi\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Google%2B-Banner-for-Nonprofi.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Google%2B-Banner-for-Nonprofi.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5.\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/company/509171\">LinkedIn Banner</a>\u00a0::\u00a0646 x 220 pixels</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-Cover-for-Nonprofi.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14134\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-Cover-for-Nonprofi.jpg?resize=600%2C204\" alt=\"LinkedIn-Cover-for-Nonprofi\" width=\"600\" height=\"204\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-Cover-for-Nonprofi.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-Cover-for-Nonprofi.jpg?resize=300%2C102&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>6. <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/nonprofitorgs\">YouTube Banner and Background</a> :: 2560 x 1440 pixels</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/YouTube-Banner-for-nonprofi.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14135\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/YouTube-Banner-for-nonprofi.jpg?resize=600%2C338\" alt=\"YouTube-Banner-for-nonprofi\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/YouTube-Banner-for-nonprofi.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/YouTube-Banner-for-nonprofi.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Graphics Designed by <a href=\"http://www.bureauforgood.com/\">Bureau for Good</a>.</p>\n",
